sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Client
  participant API as API Service
  participant PS as Redis Pub/Sub

  C->>API: GET /scoreboard/stream (SSE)<br/>Authorization: Bearer <jwt>
  API-->>C: event: snapshot / data: {top}
  API->>PS: SUBSCRIBE pubsub:scoreboard
  loop while connected
    PS-->>API: message {top, generatedAt}
    API-->>C: event: update / data: {top, generatedAt}
    Note over API,C: every 60 s
    API-->>C: event: snapshot (keep-alive)
  end
